Class VectorIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.VectorIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<VectorObject>

    public class VectorIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<VectorObject>
    A VectorObject can contain multiple sub-vectors. This iterator lets toolkit users iterate over those sub-vectors without having to access them directly.
